Package peersim.kademlia

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomDistribution
    This control initializes the whole network (that was already created by peersim) assigning a randomly generated unique NodeId to every node.
    FindOperation
    This class represents a find operation and offers the methods needed to maintain and update the closest set.
    KademliaCommonConfig
    Fixed Parameters of a kademlia network.
    KademliaObserver
    This class implements a simple observer of search time and hop average in finding a node in the network
    KademliaProtocol
    The actual protocol.
    KBucket
    This class implements a kademlia k-bucket.
    Message
    Message class provide all functionalities to manage the various messages, principally LOOKUP messages (messages from application level sender designated to another application level).
    RoutingTable
    Gives an implementation for the routing table component of a kademlia node.
    SimpleEvent
    This class defines a simple event.
    StateBuilder
    Initialization class that performs the bootsrap filling the k-buckets of all initial nodes.
    Timeout
    This class represent a timeout event.
    TrafficGenerator
    This control generates random search traffic from nodes to random destination node.
    Turbulence
    Turbulent class is only for test/statistical purpose.
    UniformRandomGenerator
    This initializator assign to the Nodes a nodeId (stored in the protocol MSPastryProtocol) by using this 128-bit (32 byte) random generator.
    Util
    Some utility and mathematical function to work with BigInteger numbers and strings.
